2. xolotl  (GPL-3.0)  — conceptual reference only, no code used
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The "Xolotl: Burst-Neuron" and "Xolotl: Half-Center-Oscillator" presets
(core/src/presets/xolotl-burst.ts, core/src/presets/xolotl-hco.ts) reproduce the
canonical single-neuron and half-centre examples of the xolotl simulator
(Gorur-Shandilya, Hoyland & Marder 2018). The maximal conductances are taken from
xolotl's published examples; the models are reimplemented in our own engine from
the underlying published equations (the Prinz channel set).

No source code from xolotl is used, copied, or derived. xolotl is licensed under
GPL-3.0; because none of its code is incorporated here, that license does not
apply to this project. This acknowledgement is provided as a courtesy.

    Reference: https://github.com/sg-s/xolotl

